1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:02,210
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,270 --> 00:00:03,480
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,280
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:05,810 --> 00:00:08,450
(Marriage Registration:
Park Tae Ho, Kim Myung Hui)

5
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:11,480
(Episode 75)

6
00:00:16,690 --> 00:00:20,460
So in the end,
you're no different...

7
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,960
from Oh Jung Ran.

8
00:00:33,670 --> 00:00:34,670
Kim Myung Hui,

9
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,740
why were you at Eunhwa Trading?

10
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:41,280
I promised you marriage...

11
00:00:42,510 --> 00:00:45,080
and access to my slush fund ledger.

12
00:00:47,190 --> 00:00:49,420
Yet, you betrayed me
and conspired with Chloe.

13
00:00:49,690 --> 00:00:51,920
For what, exactly?

14
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:04,540
This is the money
Park Cheol Su demanded.

15
00:01:08,470 --> 00:01:12,240
Give him this money and tell him
to stay overseas for a while.

16
00:01:13,410 --> 00:01:15,010
If I so much as see his shadow,

17
00:01:15,810 --> 00:01:17,780
tell him he'll never see
the light of day again.

18
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:19,580
Yes, I understand.

19
00:01:20,390 --> 00:01:21,390
Darn.

20
00:01:21,990 --> 00:01:22,990
Also, effective immediately,

21
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:27,190
I need to resume
my position as chairman.

22
00:01:27,690 --> 00:01:29,290
Yes, I'll make the arrangements.

23
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,800
Park Cheol Su.

24
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:48,040
- What do you want?
- Park Cheol Su,

25
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:51,640
you killed someone with a bomb,
didn't you?

26
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:55,550
That money in the trunk is
from Chairman Park Tae Ho of Adele.

27
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:06,420
- Hey, hold still.
- Let me go.

28
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,090
We'll make sure you get
to the police station safely.

29
00:03:08,290 --> 00:03:09,490
Darn, let go of me.

30
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,500
Darn you.

31
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:21,940
We turned Park Cheol Su over
to the police.

32
00:03:22,940 --> 00:03:25,180
Right. The intel team and I...

33
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,450
found his residence
and tipped off the police,

34
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:30,080
so they'll definitely find evidence
that he was making explosives.

35
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:33,150
Then let's request to have
Dr. Baek's accident reinvestigated.

36
00:03:33,950 --> 00:03:34,950
Okay.

37
00:03:35,490 --> 00:03:37,620
This is all thanks
to your help, Ms. Kim.

38
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:41,990
- Thank you.
- Not yet. It's too soon for that.

39
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:45,560
We have to prove
Park Tae Ho was involved.

40
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:48,700
Park Tae Ho is suspicious of me,

41
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,640
and he said
he's returning as chairman.

42
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:54,310
If Chairman Park returns,
won't he derail the investigation?

43
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:58,040
It'd be great to get him
under investigation right away.

44
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,380
That way, we could stop him
from returning as chairman.

45
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:05,180
Is there any way to get him
investigated right now?

46
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:08,150
We can't get him investigated
for what happened seven years ago,

47
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:12,020
but it might be possible on charges
related to illegal explosives.

48
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,260
That's a good idea.

49
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:16,460
I'll have the intel team report it,

50
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,860
and I'll lead the police to him.

51
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:22,230
James and I will move quickly
to get him arrested.

52
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:24,670
We'll prepare
for an emergency board meeting.

53
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:26,600
Once Chairman Park is arrested,

54
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,670
I'm going to take the position
of acting chairman.

55
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:32,140
We have to stop him from returning.

56
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:43,520
The police arrested Park Cheol Su?
How did that happen?

57
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:47,190
He said he'd lay low overseas
once he got the money!

58
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:50,430
It seems he was caught
while collecting the money.

59
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:51,530
Whatever!

60
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,330
Get our people
in the police moving...

61
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,830
before Park Cheol Su spills
what happened seven years ago.

62
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:57,840
Right now!

63
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,400
That's the thing.

64
00:05:00,170 --> 00:05:02,610
I can't get in touch
with our contacts on the force.

65
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:07,580
After you collapsed,
the payments to them stopped, and...

66
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:08,710
What?

67
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:17,960
The problem wasn't
who to entrust with the slush fund.

68
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:21,330
I should've taken care of those
who were protecting me first.

69
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:24,160
- Take the money and see them now!
- Yes, sir.

70
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:34,840
You had me thrown out like you
never wanted to see me again.

71
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,670
What do you want?

72
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:39,410
The Temi Bio incident
from seven years ago.

73
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:42,350
Does Kim Myung Hui
really know everything?

74
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,150
I told you she does.

75
00:05:44,550 --> 00:05:46,050
You finally believe me?

76
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,250
How did Kim Myung Hui find out?

77
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:50,420
Well...

78
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,360
I told her.

79
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:55,930
What?

80
00:05:57,700 --> 00:06:00,500
You were so infatuated with her
that I had no choice.

81
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:01,670
Oh Jung Ran!

82
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:07,310
Anyway, what matters is
that she knows everything.

83
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:10,010
She won't let you
get away with murder.

84
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,780
She'll turn on you...

85
00:06:11,780 --> 00:06:13,480
and make you pay for what you did.

86
00:06:15,010 --> 00:06:16,080
But me?

87
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:20,050
As long as you don't abandon me...

88
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:23,150
and make Hyun Jun your successor,

89
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:24,920
I don't care about anything else.

90
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,630
I'll even deal with Kim Myung Hui.

91
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:32,530
Can't you just give me
one more chance?

92
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,040
(Adele)

93
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,280
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

94
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:58,890
She thinks she can just
get rid of me,

95
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:01,460
Park Tae Ho of the Adele Group?

96
00:07:02,690 --> 00:07:03,800
Kim Myung Hui.

97
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:08,470
You're going to pay
for betraying me.

98
00:07:10,470 --> 00:07:11,470
Sir.

99
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:15,210
Right. Any update on Park Cheol Su?
What about our police contacts?

100
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:17,440
Well, we've got a problem.

101
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,610
You have to leave immediately.

102
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:20,140
- What?
- Hurry.

103
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,780
What's all this?

104
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,220
- You punks.
- Park Tae Ho.

105
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:29,150
You know Park Cheol Su, correct?

106
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:31,890
You're under emergency arrest
for ordering...

107
00:07:31,890 --> 00:07:33,860
the manufacture
and use of explosives.

108
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:34,930
What?

109
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,030
An emergency arrest?

110
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:40,300
You have the right to an attorney
and the right to remain silent.

111
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,300
Shut it!

112
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:45,500
Do you even know
who you're talking to?

113
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:48,640
Which precinct are you from?
What division? You punks.

114
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,370
Let go of me!

115
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:54,380
- Take him away.
- Manager Kang.

116
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,380
Find out
which precinct they're from.

117
00:07:56,450 --> 00:07:59,620
I'll make sure
they never wear a badge again.

118
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:01,320
The police or assemblymen.

119
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,050
Get someone on the line!

120
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:04,790
Let go of me.

121
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:05,920
Let go.

122
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:09,690
- Let go of me, you punks.
- Legal Team, get on this now.

123
00:08:10,330 --> 00:08:11,460
Move it.

124
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:15,970
How dare you arrest me
in my own company?

125
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:18,340
I'm Park Tae Ho of Adele!

126
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:20,070
You punks.

127
00:08:20,370 --> 00:08:23,010
You punks. Let me go.

128
00:08:23,010 --> 00:08:24,010
Sir!

129
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,090
Kim Myung Hui.

130
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:43,590
Sir.

131
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,830
You actually dared to...

132
00:08:47,530 --> 00:08:48,630
What are you talking about?

133
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,040
There's no point
in pretending you don't know.

134
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,540
I already know everything.

135
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:56,040
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

136
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:58,140
For now, please stay put.

137
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,510
I'll look into this
and handle it immediately.

138
00:09:00,650 --> 00:09:03,450
Kim Myung Hui, you...

139
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:04,580
Father!

140
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:12,690
- What is all this?
- What's happening?

141
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:16,230
He's being arrested on suspicion
of ordering the manufacture...

142
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:18,060
and use of explosives.

143
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,500
Explosives?

144
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:24,970
You two. Mobilize the legal team!

145
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,570
- Now.
- Take him.

146
00:09:26,570 --> 00:09:28,540
Let go of me. Let go!

147
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:30,540
- Let go, you punks.
- Sir!

148
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,080
- Let go!
- Sir!

149
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:37,480
Let go. Don't you know who I am?

150
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,480
Sir.

151
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:41,920
Illegal explosives? That's absurd.

152
00:09:43,890 --> 00:09:45,420
Just hang in there.

153
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:47,260
The truth...

154
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:49,660
will come out.

155
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,300
You just wait.

156
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,870
I'll expose you
for faking your amnesia...

157
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:57,740
to fool me.

158
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:01,540
Let go, you punks. Let go of me!

159
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,090
As the special July session of the
National Assembly gets underway,

160
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:15,550
the ruling and opposition parties...

161
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:18,660
remain deadlocked over a budget
and public livelihood bills.

162
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:19,660
The local elections...

163
00:10:19,690 --> 00:10:23,860
Yu Na says her case won't go
as far as a lawsuit,

164
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:29,170
but knowing Park Min Jun,
don't you think he'll sue?

165
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:30,370
Definitely.

166
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:34,570
Yu Na is kidding herself
if she thinks it won't end in a lawsuit.

167
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:38,710
Didn't she say
she'd hold her ground if he sues?

168
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:42,480
That means she's ready for a fight,
one way or another.

169
00:10:42,850 --> 00:10:45,050
Right. Then we need...

170
00:10:45,050 --> 00:10:47,220
- to be prepared.
- Of course.

171
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:51,460
Of all the lawyers we consulted,
who should we hire?

172
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,360
What about him?

173
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:54,660
Kim Genius.

174
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:58,300
- Let's go with Genius.
- Next, news on the Adele Group.

175
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,560
Adele Group Chairman Park Tae Ho
was arrested...

176
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,530
on suspicion of orchestrating
the manufacture...

177
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,900
- of illegal explosives.
- Chairman Park was arrested?

178
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,140
We have the story.

179
00:11:06,570 --> 00:11:09,940
- You've got to be kidding me.
- Adele's chairman Park Tae Ho...

180
00:11:10,010 --> 00:11:11,610
was taken into custody
for commissioning the manufacture...

181
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,480
- of illegal explosives.
- Wait. Chairman Park...

182
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,680
He did what with a bomb?

183
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:17,780
Oh my goodness.

184
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:20,350
I thought wrecking our house
was bad enough.

185
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:22,150
But bombs?

186
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,650
What did I tell you?

187
00:11:23,990 --> 00:11:25,590
Chairman Park is a dangerous man.

188
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:29,960
Oh my. What do you suppose
he used that bomb for?

189
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:32,330
Honey, could he have...

190
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:34,330
killed someone with it?

191
00:11:35,930 --> 00:11:37,100
It's only an allegation.

192
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:39,670
- What?
- Nothing's been confirmed yet,

193
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,970
so watch what you say.

194
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:44,380
- What was that?
- Are you taking his side?

195
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:47,710
I don't know.
Just don't say anything.

196
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:02,360
Park Tae Ho.

197
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:05,860
You suspect Kim Myung Hui,
so why aren't you doing anything?

198
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:10,530
I thought you'd have me
take her on again.

199
00:12:11,470 --> 00:12:13,470
Because I got the best
of you last time,

200
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,740
you won't give me another chance?

201
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:22,310
What am I supposed to do?

202
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:25,780
What do you mean?
You have to keep at it.

203
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:29,520
The plum extract has
to be made today, so hurry up.

204
00:12:30,590 --> 00:12:33,960
I don't have time to be sitting here
plucking plum stems.

205
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:35,690
Oh Jung Ran.

206
00:12:35,690 --> 00:12:39,430
From now on, your job is to sit here
plucking plum stems.

207
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:41,100
Face reality.

208
00:12:48,170 --> 00:12:49,170
What is it?

209
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,840
Who's calling?
Why are you being so secretive?

210
00:12:52,310 --> 00:12:55,550
I'm not being secretive.
I'll take this call,

211
00:12:55,610 --> 00:12:57,210
so keep plucking those stems.

212
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:00,320
If you cause trouble,
I'll report you to Ms. Kim.

213
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,620
And if you even think
about running away,

214
00:13:02,690 --> 00:13:05,660
remember that you'll never
be allowed back in.

215
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:22,610
Are you my creditor now?
Why are you here again?

216
00:13:22,970 --> 00:13:24,480
Haven't you heard?

217
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:28,380
The chairman was arrested
for something involving explosives.

218
00:13:28,780 --> 00:13:29,780
What?

219
00:13:30,350 --> 00:13:31,650
Park Tae Ho was arrested
by the police?

220
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,890
(Adele Chairman Park Arrested
on Explosives Scandal)

221
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,390
At this rate,

222
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:45,000
the Temi Bio incident from
seven years ago could be exposed.

223
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:46,060
You must've done something...

224
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:48,200
under the chairman's orders
back then, too.

225
00:13:49,530 --> 00:13:50,630
I knew it.

226
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:53,070
You were involved somehow,
weren't you?

227
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:56,370
Right. Ever since you started
blackmailing me about Temi Bio,

228
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,010
I had my suspicions.

229
00:14:00,010 --> 00:14:02,950
That's why we have to get
the chairman out.

230
00:14:03,010 --> 00:14:05,480
Not through his connections,
but through yours.

231
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:09,290
If we pull this off,
it's a huge opportunity for us.

232
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:12,520
We cover up the incident
from seven years ago...

233
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,690
and earn Park Tae Ho's trust.

234
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:16,390
Exactly.

235
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:19,230
I'll take down Park Min Jun,
and you can...

236
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:21,270
reclaim your place as his wife...

237
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:23,230
and go after President Kim.

238
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:28,140
Then we need connections powerful enough
to get Park Tae Ho released.

239
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:32,340
Maybe that guy...

240
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:35,380
Who?
Do you know someone in the police?

241
00:14:36,050 --> 00:14:39,250
I know a guy with power
who loves money.

242
00:14:39,950 --> 00:14:43,050
Then call him. No, go meet him.
Right now.

243
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,420
Wait.

244
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:47,760
But there's one big problem.

245
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,290
What's that?

246
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:50,690
Well...

247
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:52,900
I'm broke.

248
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:54,900
What?

249
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:59,200
Park Tae Ho cleared me out
when he locked me in the basement.

250
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:02,410
That guy will want
at least 100,000 dollars.

251
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:05,910
What about you?
You must have some money, right?

252
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:13,880
Were you behind my father's arrest?

253
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:16,390
Yes, that was me.

254
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:17,990
I caught the person...

255
00:15:17,990 --> 00:15:20,760
who planted the bomb
in my dad's car seven years ago.

256
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:24,600
- How?
- James helped me.

257
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:27,400
Then you should've told me.

258
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:31,840
You have enough
to deal with already.

259
00:15:32,570 --> 00:15:36,240
I didn't want to burden you
with my problems.

260
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:38,810
And I can't talk about...

261
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,550
my relationship
with President Kim yet either.

262
00:15:43,410 --> 00:15:44,420
I'm sorry.

263
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:45,880
Come on.

264
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:49,290
I'm not asking for an apology.

265
00:15:51,220 --> 00:15:53,160
I just want to help you, that's all.

266
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:55,230
I know.

267
00:15:55,990 --> 00:15:58,800
The case from seven years ago
can't be reopened just yet,

268
00:15:58,800 --> 00:15:59,930
so for now,

269
00:15:59,930 --> 00:16:02,000
Chairman Park has been charged
in connection...

270
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,270
with illegal explosives.

271
00:16:03,570 --> 00:16:06,070
Where do you go from here?

272
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:08,740
I'm not sure.

273
00:16:09,270 --> 00:16:11,780
I'll talk to James about it first.

274
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:28,690
Why do I feel so useless now?

275
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:34,030
Have you changed,
or am I the one who's changed...

276
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:39,570
now that I'm not...

277
00:16:41,370 --> 00:16:42,910
Park Tae Ho's son anymore?

278
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:55,490
What's the deal with my father?

279
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:57,990
Did you have something
to do with this?

280
00:16:58,920 --> 00:17:01,230
Yes, this was my doing.

281
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,400
With your mother's help.

282
00:17:05,060 --> 00:17:06,060
What?

283
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:11,030
Your mother found out
that I'm Baek Jin Ju.

284
00:17:14,610 --> 00:17:16,810
I wasn't going to tell you,

285
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:20,110
but I'm telling you now
because Chairman Park has been arrested.

286
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:23,050
When and how did she find out?

287
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,380
Does this mean you and my mother...

288
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:28,290
have worked out your differences enough
to work together?

289
00:17:28,290 --> 00:17:30,390
Just because I worked
with your mother...

290
00:17:30,450 --> 00:17:31,960
doesn't mean anything's changed.

291
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:37,800
Things are still over between us.

292
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:41,800
I should still stay out of it,
is that it?

293
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:45,840
I get what you mean.

294
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:50,640
If that's what you want,
I'll stay out of it.

295
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,840
Just...

296
00:17:54,910 --> 00:17:56,680
don't do anything too dangerous.

297
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:21,510
You must be here about your father.

298
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:25,110
I heard you found out
that Chloe is Jin Ju.

299
00:18:25,940 --> 00:18:26,940
How...

300
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:30,310
I heard it from Jin Ju directly.

301
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:32,980
Right.

302
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:35,390
I found out a little while ago.

303
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:37,550
I'm sorry
I couldn't tell you sooner.

304
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:41,660
It's all right.
Jin Ju probably told you not to.

305
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:46,000
She doesn't like me getting involved
in her business.

306
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:49,500
But you want to help her, don't you?

307
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:50,730
Yes.

308
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:54,810
Then quietly monitor
the legal team's response.

309
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:56,670
All right.

310
00:18:56,840 --> 00:19:00,540
I'll see to it
that Father is fully investigated.

311
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:12,590
You haven't told Min Jun
about your sister, have you?

312
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:13,690
No.

313
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:16,990
I want to tell him in my own time.

314
00:19:18,560 --> 00:19:21,530
By the way, it seems
Min Jun still has feelings...

315
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,470
for Jin Ju.

316
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:28,540
It's such a shame that
their shared fate has gone so awry.

317
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:31,170
Jin Ju's feelings are
just as important too.

318
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,740
If they're not meant to be,

319
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:36,250
then that must be fate as well.

320
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:43,220
Mr. Park.

321
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:47,690
Why did you hand
this bag of cash to Park Cheol Su?

322
00:19:47,890 --> 00:19:51,260
Come on.
I don't know anything about that.

323
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:54,400
Mr. Park Cheol Su.

324
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:57,700
You made a deal with Park Tae Ho
regarding explosives, didn't you?

325
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:00,240
I'm exercising my right
to remain silent.

326
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:09,550
Look here.
I'm Park Tae Ho of Adele Group.

327
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:12,250
When the company's lawyers get here,

328
00:20:13,620 --> 00:20:15,490
you can talk to them.

329
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:27,100
Right, Chloe. I should call her.

330
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:29,570
She's the fastest way to get money.

331
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:31,800
Not Chloe.

332
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:34,000
If we save the chairman
with her money,

333
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,640
she'll get all the credit.

334
00:20:36,610 --> 00:20:39,440
If she wins him over
and gains power,

335
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,240
do you think she'll look out for us?

336
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:44,620
The two of us have to handle this.

337
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,720
So what are you suggesting?

338
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,490
You really don't have
any money tucked away?

339
00:20:53,690 --> 00:20:57,530
Besides Chloe, is there anyone else
you can borrow money from?

340
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:02,030
Park Tae Ho cleaned me out
when all this happened.

341
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:05,200
Besides, who would lend me money
in my situation?

342
00:21:07,040 --> 00:21:08,040
Jung Ran.

343
00:21:09,910 --> 00:21:12,910
What on earth?
Wait, how did you even get in?

344
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:15,580
You wouldn't leave,

345
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:17,710
so I had to sneak in
through the crawl space.

346
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:22,190
I thought I told you to leave
Hyun Jun and Jung Ran alone.

347
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:23,590
Hold on.

348
00:21:24,150 --> 00:21:26,660
Were you spying on me?

349
00:21:26,690 --> 00:21:30,430
You're harassing both Hyun Jun
and Jung Ran, so of course...

350
00:21:30,430 --> 00:21:32,630
That's it. You.

351
00:21:38,870 --> 00:21:40,140
Mr. Song?

352
00:21:41,410 --> 00:21:44,270
What are the three of you doing?

353
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,880
First...

354
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,080
Run!

355
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:49,910
- What?
- Goodness. Oh Jung Ran, no.

356
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:52,920
Let go of me. Oh Jung Ran!

357
00:22:01,190 --> 00:22:05,960
What took you so long?
I've been waiting forever.

358
00:22:06,230 --> 00:22:08,970
So, what's the total?

359
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:12,600
This is my entire life savings.

360
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:14,070
You said Hyun Jun needed it,

361
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:15,740
so I scraped together
everything I have.

362
00:22:15,770 --> 00:22:18,540
What are you going to use
this money for?

363
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:26,950
Who are you?

364
00:22:35,930 --> 00:22:37,360
What are you doing here?

365
00:22:40,260 --> 00:22:44,200
I'm a cop sent by Mr. Park,
so you'd better start talking.

366
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:48,770
Wait. Detective Yun? From back then?

367
00:22:48,840 --> 00:22:52,310
Detective Yun?
That's ancient history.

368
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,040
I'm a high-ranking officer now.

369
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:57,080
The commissioner's right-hand man,
the second-in-command.

370
00:22:57,810 --> 00:23:00,780
Jung Ran,
you said this was for Hyun Jun,

371
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,220
so why is he...

372
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:07,560
Let's have a seat first.
Then we'll talk.

373
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:17,270
To what do I owe a visit from Adele?

374
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:21,200
You must've heard the news
about the chairman.

375
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,910
I need you to get him out.

376
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:29,210
What? Why are you using my money
to get Chairman Park out?

377
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:31,550
This is an emergency.

378
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:37,250
What do you take me for?

379
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:40,690
I'm not the same person
I used to be.

380
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:53,540
If you don't cooperate,
we'll report you for taking bribes.

381
00:23:54,910 --> 00:23:57,870
What do you all think you're doing?

382
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,340
Isn't it obvious?

383
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:02,950
Since money didn't work,
we're blackmailing you.

384
00:24:04,050 --> 00:24:08,220
Take our money,
and get the chairman out.

385
00:24:08,220 --> 00:24:11,050
Or get in trouble
for taking money from us.

386
00:24:12,460 --> 00:24:13,920
For a high-ranking police officer,

387
00:24:14,760 --> 00:24:18,330
isn't just the allegation enough
to cause a problem?

388
00:24:22,170 --> 00:24:23,670
Someone at my level...

389
00:24:25,100 --> 00:24:26,940
can have you...

390
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:30,140
all thrown in jail
for blackmailing me.

391
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:34,110
Who do you think you are, trying to
blackmail me with this chump change?

392
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:36,510
So how about it?

393
00:24:37,450 --> 00:24:41,590
Do you want to see the inside
of a holding cell?

394
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:50,560
Is this the best Adele can do?

395
00:24:53,530 --> 00:24:54,530
Wait.

396
00:24:58,770 --> 00:25:00,970
What if we up the scale?

397
00:25:03,770 --> 00:25:06,180
Think of this
as just a down payment.

398
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:09,480
If you get the chairman out,
he'll make sure...

399
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,950
you're compensated properly.

400
00:25:12,620 --> 00:25:13,720
That's right.

401
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,990
Do you think that's all he'll do?

402
00:25:16,490 --> 00:25:18,820
The Adele Group could
have your back, you know.

403
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:21,120
Second-in-command, are you?

404
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:25,230
Becoming number one would be
a piece of cake.

405
00:25:28,370 --> 00:25:29,370
Deal?

406
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:43,780
You told Min Jun
we worked together, right?

407
00:25:45,020 --> 00:25:47,620
Yes. Since Chairman Park
was arrested,

408
00:25:48,020 --> 00:25:50,150
I felt it was time to tell him.

409
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:54,620
But that doesn't mean Min Jun
is going to work with us.

410
00:25:55,230 --> 00:25:59,230
I already told him
to stay out of my business.

411
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:02,530
Right, that's what he told me.

412
00:26:06,770 --> 00:26:08,610
I just heard from Butler Ok.

413
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:10,410
Oh Jung Ran escaped.

414
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:13,080
She did what?

415
00:26:13,540 --> 00:26:16,280
- How?
- I don't know the details,

416
00:26:17,750 --> 00:26:20,350
but she left with Choi Yu Na
and Driver Song.

417
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:23,050
After hearing about
Chairman Park's arrest,

418
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,850
don't you think
they're up to something?

419
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:28,220
I'll look into it.

420
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:32,860
I planted a bug in the annex
to keep an eye on Oh Jung Ran.

421
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:34,100
A listening device?

422
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:36,930
Then we might be able to find out
what Oh Jung Ran...

423
00:26:36,930 --> 00:26:38,270
and Choi Yu Na are plotting.

424
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:43,110
Yes, I'll go in and see
if anything was recorded.

425
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:44,840
Okay.

426
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:46,710
How's the police investigation
going?

427
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:50,310
Park Cheol Su and Chairman Park
aren't saying anything.

428
00:26:50,810 --> 00:26:52,550
And since
there's no other solid evidence,

429
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:55,950
they could be released
within 48 hours.

430
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:58,690
The emergency board meeting is
still on for tomorrow, right?

431
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:02,360
Yes. I'm going to be appointed
as acting chairman.

432
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,690
I'll try to convince the board
and the shareholders...

433
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:06,260
to keep Chairman Park
from coming back.

434
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,240
What?

435
00:27:17,370 --> 00:27:18,380
Moon Tae Jin,

436
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,780
the largest shareholder,
is recommending me for that?

437
00:27:19,940 --> 00:27:21,040
That's right.

438
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:24,410
He...

439
00:27:24,910 --> 00:27:29,250
must've seen the news
about Chairman Park's arrest.

440
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:31,620
Chairman Park is involved
in a crime,

441
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:32,660
and on top of that,

442
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:34,990
he and Oh Jung Ran...

443
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:38,500
have filed for divorce.

444
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:42,830
Given the circumstances,
he suggested that instead...

445
00:27:43,330 --> 00:27:47,900
of serving as acting chairman,
you take the chairman's seat.

446
00:27:48,770 --> 00:27:51,170
Me, as chairman?

447
00:27:51,610 --> 00:27:54,140
If you're going to fight
Park Tae Ho and Oh Jung Ran...

448
00:27:54,810 --> 00:27:57,550
and you're determined
to take over the Adele Group,

449
00:27:58,920 --> 00:28:00,720
isn't this a great opportunity?

450
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:03,950
If you're determined to do this,

451
00:28:04,150 --> 00:28:08,160
Moon Tae Jin will throw
his full support behind you.

452
00:28:09,290 --> 00:28:12,500
Please don't take
too long to decide.

453
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,340
Not Chloe.

454
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:23,740
If we save the chairman
with her money,

455
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:25,410
she'll get all the credit.

456
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:28,750
If she wins him over
and gains power,

457
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,350
do you think she'll look out for us?

458
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:34,050
The two of us have to handle this.

459
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:42,230
Oh Jung Ran and Choi Yu Na plan
to buy Chairman Park's freedom.

460
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:45,800
If he gets out scot-free
and comes back...

461
00:29:19,860 --> 00:29:22,530
I was going to ask you
before I hung it up.

462
00:29:22,970 --> 00:29:24,930
I didn't want to get ahead
of myself again,

463
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:27,970
like I did when I proposed.

464
00:29:30,610 --> 00:29:33,740
You know there's
an emergency board meeting...

465
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:34,810
tomorrow morning, right?

466
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:38,480
Yes. I heard President Kim is
going to be the acting chairman.

467
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:41,350
What's your plan?
What do you need me to do?

468
00:29:42,050 --> 00:29:44,550
Skip the board meeting tomorrow...

469
00:29:45,220 --> 00:29:46,360
and talk to me instead.

470
00:29:47,190 --> 00:29:49,390
About what?
Can't we talk about it now?

471
00:29:50,030 --> 00:29:52,130
No. We'll talk tomorrow morning.

472
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:56,970
I still have a few things
to take care of.

473
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,770
Once I'm done,

474
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:03,340
we'll hang this photo together.

475
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:28,030
You want me to become the chairman,
not just the acting chairman?

476
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:36,240
Jin Ju is saying the same thing
Mrs. Han said.

477
00:30:36,870 --> 00:30:39,380
I found out about Oh Jung Ran
and Choi Yu Na's plan...

478
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:41,180
from the bug I planted in the annex.

479
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,880
They're using police connections
and even money...

480
00:30:44,310 --> 00:30:45,950
to get Chairman Park out.

481
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:49,350
If Chairman Park gets out scot-free,

482
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:51,250
it'll be hard to stop him
from returning as chairman.

483
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:56,060
It'd be better for you to take
the chairman's seat yourself.

484
00:30:56,690 --> 00:30:58,090
Then even if Chairman Park returns,

485
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,860
it'll be difficult for him
to retake the position.

486
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:02,570
But isn't that different
from your plan?

487
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:05,440
For now, we have to stop
Chairman Park from coming back.

488
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:08,840
As things stand,
neither you, Hyun Jun,

489
00:31:09,340 --> 00:31:12,380
nor I are qualified to be chairman.

490
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:15,310
If we don't want Chairman Park
back in that seat,

491
00:31:16,550 --> 00:31:18,050
you're our best option, Ms. Kim.

492
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,180
I agree with Jin Ju.

493
00:31:21,320 --> 00:31:23,790
Mother, are you good with this?

494
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,390
All right, let's do it.

495
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:35,130
(Emergency Board Meeting,
Chairman Appointment)

496
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,300
The Adele Group...

497
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:38,970
emergency board meeting
will now begin.

498
00:31:39,300 --> 00:31:42,240
Today's agenda concerns
the appointment...

499
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:44,110
of President Kim Myung Hui
as chairman.

500
00:31:44,770 --> 00:31:48,540
First, we'll hear
from President Kim Myung Hui.

501
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,310
How dare you...

502
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:22,880
try to replace me as chairman?

503
00:32:51,210 --> 00:32:54,110
(Pearl in Red)

504
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:57,310
Now I finally see what you're
really after, Kim Myung Hui.

505
00:32:57,310 --> 00:33:01,120
How dare you try to push me out
and take my seat as chairman?

506
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:02,350
You're making a mistake.

507
00:33:02,350 --> 00:33:03,990
You're putting Oh Jung Ran
in my place?

508
00:33:04,090 --> 00:33:05,150
You'll regret it.

509
00:33:05,150 --> 00:33:08,690
If I use Hyun Jun's weakness
to marry into the Adele family,

510
00:33:09,090 --> 00:33:12,060
both he and Adele will be mine.

511
00:33:12,630 --> 00:33:14,630
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
